---
import Container from "./util/Container.astro";
import Timeline from "./Timeline.astro";
import Headings from "./util/Headings.astro";
---

<Container id="about">
  <Headings><span>about me</span>( )</Headings>
  <div
    class="flex flex-col justify-between max-lg:space-y-8 lg:flex-row-reverse lg:items-center"
  >
    <picture class="max-xl:mx-auto">
      <img
        src="/pixlr-img.webp"
        class="size-60 rounded-full border-2 border-violet-600/60 shadow-[0_0px_50px_-15px_rgb(0,0,0,0.25)] shadow-violet-600/75 md:size-72 xl:size-80 2xl:size-96"
        alt="Picture of myself"
      />
    </picture>

    <article class="space-y-4 text-lg lg:max-w-lg xl:max-w-xl xl:text-xl">
      <p class="text-pretty text-start max-2xl:lg:mr-14">
        Originally from <strong class="font-bold text-mainGreen"
          >Dominican Republic</strong
        >, I have resided in USA for the past six years. High school education
        was completed in Texas, followed by a move to <strong
          class="font-bold text-mainGreen">Lynn, Massachusetts</strong
        >, for college studies.
      </p>

      <p class="text-pretty text-start max-2xl:lg:mr-14">
        A childhood fascination with computers sparked my passion for
        programming. While game development was initially explored, <strong
          class="font-bold text-mainGreen">web development</strong
        > emerged as a captivating field. This journey has deepened a commitment
        to crafting impactful digital experiences through web development.
      </p>

      <p class="text-pretty text-start max-2xl:lg:mr-14">
        Graduated from North Shore Community College with a major in <strong
          class="font-bold text-mainGreen">Computer Science</strong
        >. The coursework provided a strong foundation in computer science
        principles, various programming languages, and effective problem-solving
        techniques.
      </p>
    </article>
  </div>
</Container>

<Timeline />
